              <p>Do you want to tell other people you are proudly a member of FrozenFlower? Or do you want to have a link to FrozenFlower? A great way to do it is with the FrozenFlower button. Just include this html:</p>
              <p>&lt;a href="http://frozenflower.net" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img src="http://frozenflower.net/images/frozen-flower.png" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</p>
              <p>And you'll get something like this:</p>
              <p><a href="http://frozenflower.net"><img src="http://frozenflower.net/images/frozen-flower.png" border="0"/></a></p>
              <p>Another idea would be to use a text link.</p>
